VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (\bvalidateInput\s*=\s*['"]false['"])
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:validateRequest\s*=\s*"false"|@SuppressWarnings.*"unchecked"|@Valid\s*=\s*false|disableValidation && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects disabled input validation in Java code.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Disabled Input Validation.
